original_title: CeCe Winans: Live in the Throne Room
overview: Recorded before an enthusiastic crowd of worshippers at Cornerstone Church in Madison, Cece Winans and her electrifying five-piece band and singers presented a set list that include music from her praise and worship CD "Throne Room" as well as popular songs from her vast repertoire.
title: CeCe Winans: Live in the Throne Room
